<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN220-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉ vaṭakkiruntāṉaiyuḻaic ceṉṟu mīṇṭuvantu uṟaiyūrkaṇṭa pottiyār aḻutu pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN220">
<l>peruñcōṟu payantu palyāṇṭu puranta</l>
<l>peruṅkaḷi ṟiḻanta paitaṟ pāka</l>
<l>ṉatucērn talkiya vaḻuṅka lālai</l>
<l>veḷilpā ḻākka kaṇṭukaluḻn tāṅkuk</l>
<l>kalaṅkiṉe ṉallaṉō yāṉē polantārt</l>
<l>tērvaṇ kiḷḷi pōkiya</l>
<l>pēricai mūtūr maṉṟaṅ kaṇṭē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="2">A suffering mahout who has lost a big elephant bull </l>
<l corresp="1">he had protected for many years, pouring [it] great rice, </l>
<l corresp="4">weeping like [him] when seeing that the post is in ruin </l>
<l corresp="3">in the noisy stables where it had rested joined to it, </l>
<l corresp="5a-c">was I not upset, I, </l>
<l corresp="7">when seeing the central place of the famous ancient town </l>
<l corresp="5d-6">from which Kiḷḷi, generous with chariots [and] golden garlands, went [away]? </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
